  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Buffet breakfast </p>
<p>Half Board includes breakfast and dinner and beverages (1/2 a litre of water and a 1/4 litre of house wine) and can be enjoyed in the buffet restaurant.</p>
<p><strong>Blue Naxos Formula</strong> can be combined with all room types, providing additional facilities such as: exclusive breakfast at "Casa del Massaro" or “Stella di Mare” restaurants from 08.00 to 10.30 am, buffet dinner in a reserved area of the sea front "Stella di Mare" restaurant or “Casa del Massaro” restaurant, one beach towel per person and a kettle with a selection of teas. The Blue Naxos Formula is available at a supplement between 30 May - 11 Sep 20 on request, please call to book.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
