  <description><![CDATA[<p>Surrounded by a natural landscape and set amidst citrus and olive groves, the Naxos Beach Resort is a beautiful retreat situated right on the beachfront in Giardini Naxos. The complex offers a wide variety of activities to entertain the whole family during your stay. Those feeling active can choose from the likes of windsurfing, basketball and tennis. If you're looking to relax you'll also be spoiled for choice as you can chill on the large sun terrace beside one of the resort's two pools whilst enjoying a cool drink from Del Parco Bar, or relax on a comfortable lounger by the sea on the hotel's private beach. The resort is in a great location to explore the impressive sights of <a data-udi="umb://document/b037a20c14a3421ba33b32859c9e3344" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b037a20c14a3421ba33b32859c9e3344}" title="Sicily">Sicily</a>. The stunning volcano, <em>Mount Etna</em>, is just an hour's drive away and can be seen from the hotel and the lovely historic town of <a data-udi="umb://document/919b72992bd64fd4a35a60df994feff6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/919b72992bd64fd4a35a60df994feff6}" title="Taormina Area">Taormina</a> is just a 25-minute drive away.</p>
<p>The hotel offers guests a choice of restaurants. Try the delicious fresh fish from Stella di Mare, right on the beach front, or for a traditional atmosphere and Sicilian delicacies the Casa Del Massaro restaurant serves an à la carte menu in a farmhouse setting. The comfortable and elegant guest rooms provide a relaxing retreat.</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 50 mins by private car from Catania Airport </p>]]></description>
