  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Restaurants &amp; Bars</strong></span><span style="text-decoration: underline;"></span></p>
<p><strong>Oasys Restaurant</strong> is an elegant buffet restaurant that serves breakfast, lunch and dinner and can be found in the main building. Guests can dine on the covered terrace overlooking the gardens.</p>
<p><strong>Del Parco Restaurant </strong>has a central location and serves a buffet breakfast, lunch and dinner. Guests have to option to dine in the winter garden. </p>
<p><strong>Stella di Mare Restaurant </strong>is the hotel's beach side restaurant offering guests an à la carte lunch menu, specialising in typical Sicilian cuisine, including delicately flavored fresh fish. For evening meals there is a buffet service. (Open during the high season only) This is the dinner option for the blue Naxos Formula. </p>
<p><strong>Casa del Massaro Restauaunt </strong>The restaurant is located in the renovated traditional Sicilian farmhouse. Reserve a table an enjoy a traditional Sicilian style meal by candle light. A buffet breakfast is served here for the Blue Naxos Formula Guests from 8:00am to 10:30am. (Open during the high season only) </p>
<p><strong>Il'Cucciolo Restaurant</strong> is dedicated to the younger guests serving nutritional meals for childeren up to 6 years old.</p>
<p><strong>Calypso</strong> is the hotel's main bar, located on the “Piazzetta”, the heart of the Resort. Open from morning until late night, is the ideal place for rendez-vous, tasting home-made ice cream and “Granita” and to take part in various entertainment activities. During the evening shows and games are open to all Guests.</p>
<p><strong>Olympus Cafe </strong>is a piano bar with live music and serves a wide selection of drinks. </p>
<p><strong>Stella di Mare</strong> serves drinks and has various different events taking place throughout the season</p>
<p><strong>Del Parco</strong> serves a delicious array of cocktails, and is located by the Olympic pool. </p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<p><strong>Sport activities</strong> available free of charge include the fitness center, two illuminated tennis courts (reservations is compulsory). Guests can also take part in water sports: sailing, windsurf, canoe and Other sports such as archery, volleyball, basketball, table tennis, aerobics, swimming, dancing lessons, petanque and bowling with collective courses.</p>
<ul>
<li>Two outdoor swimming pools</li>
<li>Evening entertainment</li>
<li>Private beach (Payable locally. Price included for all inclusive guests) </li>
<li>Free wifi</li>
<li>Parking </li>
<li>On site shops </li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
