  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms</strong> are found in the hotel's main building. They are around 23m² and furnished in an elegant style. Facilities include Satellite TV, mini fridge, safe, free wifi, hairdryer and complimentary toiletries. Nestled within the gardens are villas that have their own patio area furnished with table and two chairs, where you can take in the beautiful surrounding gardens. These rooms sleep two people with the possibility of adding an extra bed for children on request (payable locally for approx. €8 per day or €50 per week). </p>
<p><strong>Villa Superior Double Rooms </strong>are surrounded by the luscious gardens and decorated in in an elegant style. These rooms are located on the ground floor and the first floor. The rooms have either a terrace or balcony. </p>
<p><strong>Villa Superior Triple Rooms </strong>are located on the ground floor. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Villa Superior Family Rooms </strong>consisting of two rooms (one of which smaller with two single beds for children) and one bathroom. These rooms are located on the first floor. Interconnecting rooms are available. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Executive Rooms </strong>are located in the main building and have a balcony overlooking the sea<strong><span>. </span></strong>These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms </strong>have side sea views and sleep two people. They are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Single Occupancy </strong>Classic Rooms and Superior rooms are are available for single use on request, please call to book</p>]]></roomsDescription>
